  "description": "China National Chemical Engineering Co., Ltd. engages in the chemical engineering business in China. It is involved in the contracting of construction engineering, petrochemicals, coal chemical industry, fine chemicals, pharmaceuticals, electric power, environmental ecological protection, infrastructure engineering and overseas engineering; and engineering consulting, surveying, design, construction, and project management and services. The company also engages in the provision of engineering supervision services; technology research and development and promotion of results; manufacturing and installation of complete sets of pipelines, lines and equipment; quality inspection technical services; import and export business; and machinery and equipment leasing. In addition, it is involved in investment and management of industrial equipment and infrastructure; dispatching labor personnel required for the implementation of overseas engineering projects; and sale of electrical equipment. The company was founded in 1953 and is based in Beijing, China. China National Chemical Engineering Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of China National Chemical Engineering Group Corporation Ltd.",
